      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your bond to nature strengthens, bringing with it new magical talents.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Wis 13, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.JKpzGsTrTkZZpmFq]{Minor Naturalism}, character level 4th.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Select one of the following 1st-level spells: @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.kzOemsOWuqgbbGZw]{baleful polymorph} (Alien Archive 2 147), @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.uk49OnFMhCg9CSv1]{detect radiation}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.dIlKtUGGKcur6OaK]{wisp ally}. You can cast this spell once per day as a spell-like ability, using your character level as your caster level. The key ability score for this spell is Wisdom.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> You can select this feat more than once. Each time you do, you must choose a different spell from the list.</p>"
